               <t:note>
                  <t:date type="foundation" notBefore="1500" notAfter="1600">1500-1600</t:date>
                  <t:desc type="foundation">Local tradition tells that the religious site existed before the advent of Christianity.</t:desc>
                  <t:ab type="history">Dabr. The old church stands outside the sity; the recent church associated with Qandāʿro Qirqos has been built close to the city.  
</t:ab>
                  <t:ab type="description">
