                        </t:graphic>
                     </t:figure>15 Mss. photographed: <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq001">QDQ-001</t:ref> “Four Gospels”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq002">QDQ-002</t:ref> “The Rite of the Holy Week”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq003">QDQ-003</t:ref> “The Book of the Epistle; Miracles of Mary; Miracles of Libanos”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq004">QDQ-004</t:ref> “Synaxarion (September - August)”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq005">QDQ-005</t:ref> “Vita of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq006">QDQ-006</t:ref> “Vita of Cyriacus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq007">QDQ-007</t:ref> “Miracles of Jesus; Vita of St. George”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq008">QDQ-008</t:ref> “Vita of Täklä Haymanot”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq009">QDQ-009</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq010">QDQ-010</t:ref> “Synoptic Lectionary for the Year”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq011">QDQ-011</t:ref> “Vita of Abunä Arägawi”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq012">QDQ-012</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq013">QDQ-013</t:ref> “The Book of the Story of the Trinity”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq014">QDQ-014</t:ref> “The Book of the Matrimony Rite”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESqdq015">QDQ-015</t:ref> “Missal”.</t:ab>
     
